 Designers around the world are creating economy and premium economy seats that are comfier and provide more legroom .
Crawley-based Acro Aircraft Seating recently unveiled the design for its new premium economy seat .
Acro 's ` Series 7 ' seat has hand-stitched leather armrests , an aluminium chassis and composite materials .
The seats were designed to eliminate the sources of discomfort and more more space for the occupants .